close_reason: "Resolved by skipping nested host CLI installs for npm package extensions, linking @unbrained/pm-cli to the active host package root, preserving package runtime metadata, updating SDK/package docs, updating @sentry/node to 10.59.0, and verifying with focused tests, manual temp smoke, full 100/100/100/100 coverage, static/contracts/security/changelog/Sentry/telemetry gates."
